# Bitcoin Price Prediction

## Objective
To predict Bitcoin price trends using historical market data and machine learning / time series models.

## Problem Statement
Cryptocurrency prices are highly volatile, making prediction important for investors and analysts.

## Tools Used
- Python
- Pandas, NumPy
- Scikit-learn / LSTM / ARIMA
- Power BI

## Workflow
- Data collection and preprocessing
- Feature engineering
- Model building
- Forecasting

## Output
- Predicted Bitcoin price trends
- Visual comparison of actual vs predicted values

